            <Col id="commonTitle07">&lt;fs v='9'&gt;STEP 03&lt;/fs&gt; Guidelines on school violence prevention and report</Col>
            <Col id="commonTitle09">&lt;br&gt;&lt;center&gt;&amp;lt;School Violence&amp;gt;&lt;/center&gt;&lt;br&gt;School violence is causing difficulty to a student by another person inside and/or outside the school by carrying out the following actions.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Using profanities, teasing or threatening, forcing another to run errands, taking of money or property, hitting a friend's body or forcefully confining in a location, sexual molestation, sexual harassment or sexual assault, cyber-bullying (internet or smart-phone), continuously harassing someone, continuously rejecting someone, etc.&lt;/b&gt;</Col>
            <Col id="commonTitle10">&lt;br&gt;&lt;center&gt;&amp;lt;School Violence&amp;gt;&lt;/center&gt;&lt;br&gt;School violence is causing difficulty to a student by another person inside and/or outside the school by carrying out the following actions.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Using profanities, teasing or threatening, forcing another to run errands, taking of money or property, hitting a friend's body or forcefully confining in a location, sexual molestation, sexual harassment or sexual assault, cyber-bullying (internet or smart-phone), continuously harassing someone, continuously rejecting someone, etc.&lt;/b&gt;</Col>
            <Col id="commonTitle11">&lt;br&gt;&lt;center&gt;&amp;lt;School Violence&amp;gt;&lt;/center&gt;&lt;br&gt;School violence is causing difficulty to a student by another person inside and/or outside the school by carrying out the following actions.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Using profanities, teasing or threatening, forcing another to run errands, taking of money or property, hitting a friend's body or forcefully confining in a location, sexual molestation, sexual harassment or sexual assault, cyber-bullying (internet or smart-phone), continuously harassing someone, continuously rejecting someone, etc.&lt;/b&gt;</Col>
